{"tid":1567611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國白宮聯署更新上線喇！","createTime":"2019-09-14T06:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T06:21:12.000Z","uid":258680,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"96e93f8d99d7775ee804e358ebf9a3d4b8fe3c38","tid":1567611,"uid":258680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:34:33.000Z","msg":"原文link <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=391692284750253&amp;id=115540999032051\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D391692284750253%26id%3D115540999032051&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ9ey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=e4e64702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=391692284750253&amp;id=115540999032051</a><br />\n<br />\n【恕我沒有心情講中秋快樂】<br />\n最近有網友畀咗個方法我，利用一啲詭計產生大量email address，唔使確認簽署都可以計到數。好抱歉，越過我底線了，我明白大家都好想個聯署人數快啲達標，但我都希望件事會係正直地完成。<br />\n<br />\n先唔講咁樣做，係咪真係呃得到白宮，如果呃唔到，個聯署會唔會作廢。如果，要搵十萬個人簽關於香港嘅聯署，都要使詐先可以完成，咁其實呢個地方仲有冇得救？<br />\n<br />\n所以我依然相信，條數上得唔夠快，係因為好多人唔知有呢啲聯署，我哋嘅責任係令佢哋知，唔係篤數。你篤數嘅話，同中國人有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n簽＞等電郵＞確認簽署＞叫十個朋友簽<br />\n<br />\n🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸《未夠數》🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸<br />\n==========<br />\n如香港政府實施緊急法，請美國廢除《香港政策法》<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-abolish-united-states-hong-kong-policy-act-if-hong-kong-implement-emergency-regulations-ordinance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-abolish-united-states-hong-kong-policy-act-if-hong-kong-implement-emergency-regulations-ordinance&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ9ey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=2d1221ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-abolish-united-states-hong-kong-policy-act-if-hong-kong-implement-emergency-regulations-ordinance</a><br />\n//<br />\n請求美國派美軍拯救香港巿民 (Deadline Oct 11)<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-c